{"tid":2053212,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"其實係移民外國真係比起留係香港好？","createTime":"2020-06-06T05:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T00:55:12.000Z","uid":119864,"like":7,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"aaa33b0b9e9256dd2780b733a5322c74065f54b5","tid":2053212,"uid":119864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:41:32.000Z","msg":"香港有樓有份好工既想移民既有幾多？<br />\n去到外國要重新適應生活同搵新工作，好似好多三字頭以上既未必真係會想移民，有都係等小朋友上到中學就要佢留學，而自己留係香港搵食同供樓<br />\n<br />\n好多人一動不如一靜<br />\n老共又識溫水煮蛙高壓懷柔<br />\n而且只要人工高又會有人才填補<br />\n未來香港應該唔會比依加差得咁緊要"},{"pid":"0e1c63b602f6dcb3ab217fe242b20298400f2cee","tid":2053212,"uid":231583,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:43:25.000Z","msg":"老共又識溫水煮蛙高壓懷柔<br />\n<br />\n此po已完"},{"pid":"c210b4eb69e6e22c663b753573436a9424493cde","tid":2053212,"uid":250550,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:46:40.000Z","msg":"就算唔係真移民 起埋攞本外國護照再住香港<br />\n所謂狡兔三窟<br />\n護照多本外國嘅，銀行戶口遍佈幾個國家<br />\n有啲做生意嘅就可以開拓埋海外市場<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd37810bc5e4aad5491e99de7dec85fe616ef48","tid":2053212,"uid":60635,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"0e1c63b602f6dcb3ab217fe242b20298400f2cee","tid":2053212,"uid":231583,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:43:25.000Z","msg":"老共又識溫水煮蛙高壓懷柔<br />\n<br />\n此po已完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:47:56.000Z","msg":"中共玩到無左一座金融中心，全民擺地攤。<br />\n邊忽温水煮蛙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢而家係燒紅D油加凍水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c0b3346f07fa2e8d03e2105bf6624885db067a","tid":2053212,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:57:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\">總加速師</span></em></strong></span>個名你估浪得虛名架？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n攬炒小學加速師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757ee962f332540eba21ee9254ce74a91cdf3e45","tid":2053212,"uid":119864,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e1c63b602f6dcb3ab217fe242b20298400f2cee","tid":2053212,"uid":231583,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T05:43:25.000Z","msg":"老共又識溫水煮蛙高壓懷柔<br />\n<br />\n此po已完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:04:49.000Z","msg":"之前係溫水煮蛙，呢幾年係明顯左"},{"pid":"0f00271ab74e4c39f39c604b7e5abc85d635df00","tid":2053212,"uid":82717,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:05:08.000Z","msg":"如果好似我家境麻麻 算草根階層嘅話<br />\n我覺得自己好易滿足 覺得移民係做得好啱嘅決定<br />\n<br />\n我去咗好多人都話消費高嘅sf bay area<br />\n細個屋企住公屋 走之前買咗樓 而家住獨立屋 <br />\n依邊天氣正到爆 <br />\n生活方便 工作環境真係好正<br />\n有campus 唔使受氣 福利好 人工高<br />\n後院唔大佔地6000尺 可以種下野<br />\n而家屋企兩大一小 兩架車<br />\n<br />\n身邊都唔少朋友三字頭先移民 個個都覺得生活好滿足"},{"pid":"be8c93df535ac05a6964ba02aef76e94c8f11ecc","tid":2053212,"uid":37869,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:15:47.000Z","msg":"未來香港應該唔會比依加差得咁緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇黎你唔相信一個獨裁政權可以有幾恐怖<br />\n我唔係話中共必定極恐怖<br />\n但我相信將會向住呢個方向發展"},{"pid":"7063585406f4d0b2afefd8490136685be384e66e","tid":2053212,"uid":118226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f00271ab74e4c39f39c604b7e5abc85d635df00","tid":2053212,"uid":82717,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:05:08.000Z","msg":"如果好似我家境麻麻 算草根階層嘅話<br />\n我覺得自己好易滿足 覺得移民係做得好啱嘅決定<br />\n<br />\n我去咗好多人都話消費高嘅sf bay area<br />\n細個屋企住公屋 走之前買咗樓 而家住獨立屋 <br />\n依邊天氣正到爆 <br />\n生活方便 工作環境真係好正<br /